des: Dry cleaning and laundry has never been easier! Simply have Alexa tell Champion Cleaners to "Schedule a pick up" and Alexa will let you know when your next driver will be by. The Champion Cleaners kill for Amazon Alexa now makes it super simple for you to experience Cleaner, Simpler, Happier - Delivered. Try it today!
